  "remarks": "Director of the University and the Higher National Defence Research Institute since 20 Sep 2021. Former Senior Advisor for Security Affairs to the Chief of the Armed Forces General Staff. Chief of Iran's National Police from 2005 until early 2015. Also Head of the Iranian Cyber Police (EU-listed) from Jan 2011 until early 2015. Forces under his command led brutal attacks on peaceful protests and a violent night-time attack on the dormitories of Tehran University on 15 Jun 2009. Former head of Iran's Headquarters in support of the Yemeni People.",
